{"tid":1056341,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"同市光榮，皇馬望祖記與C.朗被淘汰","createTime":"2019-03-11T06:41:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-13T01:56:17.000Z","uid":173952,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"072df2e204779e8afb2e599aeb186302fef3f9b9","tid":1056341,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T06:41:39.000Z","msg":"據足球市場網援引西班牙電視六台報導，雖然皇馬已經遭到淘汰，但部分皇馬球員仍希望同城死敵馬體會能夠在歐聯中擊敗祖記和C.朗拿度。<br />\n<br />\n  祖雲達斯首回合在作客0-2不敵馬體會，下週中回到主場他們必須克服重重難關才能晉級8強。<br />\n<br />\n  此前有消息稱皇馬不想在歐聯8強遭遇祖雲達斯和C.朗拿度，因此他們都支持同城死敵馬體會擊敗對手。<br />\n<br />\n  而雖然皇馬現在已被阿積士淘汰，但據西班牙電視六台報導，西班牙記者伊度亞度-因達表示有部分皇馬球員仍希望祖記和C.朗拿度被淘汰，他們支持球隊的同城死敵馬德里體育會最終獲勝。"},{"pid":"c107a245bb877087c015de7a5f70ffc92a08f2ab","tid":1056341,"uid":65743,"like":24,"dislike":4,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T06:44:45.000Z","msg":"今鋪我撐阿朗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d55784ebe6ece43020c5e68d2fe8e9dbe54d5192","tid":1056341,"uid":217374,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T06:46:34.000Z","msg":"幾似某啲球迷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e9d8037e4ca4ccc9040fd733718f6a8a2d79263","tid":1056341,"uid":46890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T06:47:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bb54c8a2607dfab014e3b2ed54901cb7e5ddbf3","tid":1056341,"uid":38172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T06:48:33.000Z","msg":"魚蛋論又中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1354d6799e8c9ffca25f27c46452669da46a078d","tid":1056341,"uid":59737,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T06:49:47.000Z","msg":"蝗馬教你咩你係足球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a278d18